               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I gave her the half-crown, not knowing it was Bad, and she gave me the 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. The Friday afterwards, I changed a half<lb></lb>sovereign, and went to get something for my Breakfast; the woman took the half-crown, and went out, and afterwards came back and said it was Bad. I said I would give her 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. to make up for it; she would not take it, but would give mein custody. There was a crowd round the door; and the woman gave the crowd the two half-crowns tolook at. That afterwards, the policeman came, and she gave them to him; he asked her if she had marked them, and she said, "No;" and he said, "Then you ought to mark them;" and he marked them in the shop, and then I went with him to the station.</p>
